Class Structure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestlabs.sdk.Structure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    public final class Structure
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Structure represents and contains all properties of a Nest structure.

      • getAway

        public String getAway()
        Returns the away state of the structure. In order for a structure to be in the Auto-Away state, all devices must also be in Auto-Away state. When any device leaves the Auto-Away state, then the structure also leaves the Auto-Away state.

        Values can be "home", "away", or "auto-away"

        Returns:
        the away state of the structure.
